## Bundled Vocabulary Components

Geoff includes curated subsets of the following open vocabularies, each with its own license:

### 1. Schema.org (ontologies/schema-org.ttl)
**License:** Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 (CC BY-SA 3.0)
**Source:** https://schema.org/ (Release 28.0, 2025)
**Attribution:** "Portions of this work are based on schema.org, used under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 License."

The schema.org subset included in Geoff contains selected terms relevant to web content publishing (Article, BlogPosting, WebPage, WebSite, HowTo, etc.) with their definitions, comments, and human-readable labels.

### 2. Dublin Core (ontologies/dublin-core.ttl)
**License:** Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
**Source:** https://www.dublincore.org/ (Dublin Core Metadata Initiative)
**Attribution:** "Portions of this work are based on Dublin Core Metadata Terms, used under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License."

### 3. FOAF — Friend of a Friend (ontologies/foaf.ttl)
**License:** Creative Commons Attribution 1.0 (CC BY 1.0)
**Source:** https://xmlns.com/foaf/spec/
**Attribution:** "Portions of this work are based on the Friend of a Friend vocabulary, used under the Creative Commons Attribution 1.0 License."

### 4. SIOC — Semantically Interlinked Online Communities (ontologies/sioc.ttl)
**License:** Creative Commons Attribution (CC BY) + W3C Document License
**Source:** http://sioc-project.org/
**Attribution:** "Portions of this work are based on the SIOC Core Ontology, used under the Creative Commons Attribution License."

